import React from "react";
import { Accordion, ListGroup } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";

const MobileFooterNav = () => {
    <Accordion defaultActiveKey="0" flush>
        <Accordion.Item eventKey="0">
            <Accordion.Header>
                More about <Link to='/'>E-Shop</Link>
            </Accordion.Header>
            <Accordion.Body>
                <ListGroup variant="flush">
                    <Link to='/'><ListGroup.Item>ABOUT US</ListGroup.Item></Link>
                    <Link to='/'><ListGroup.Item>POLICY</ListGroup.Item></Link>
                    <Link to='/'><ListGroup.Item>FAQs</ListGroup.Item></Link>
                    <Link to='/'><ListGroup.Item>CONTACT</ListGroup.Item></Link>
                    <Link to='/'><ListGroup.Item>JOIN US</ListGroup.Item></Link>
                </ListGroup>
            </Accordion.Body>

        </Accordion.Item>
    </Accordion>
}

export default MobileFooterNav;
